 </para>

 <sect1 xml:id="sec-ay-docupdates-sle15-sp0">
  <title>&productname; 15 SP0</title>
  <para/>

  <sect2 xml:id="sec-ay-docupdates-sle15-sp0-jan-2019">
   <title>January 2019</title>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><xref linkend="CreateProfile-firewall-general"/></term>
     <listitem>
      <itemizedlist>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         Added a description of the parameters <varname>target</varname>,
         <varname>name</varname>, <varname>short</varname>, and
         <varname>description</varname>.
        </para>
       </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect2>
  <sect2 xml:id="sec-ay-docupdates-sle15-sp0-dec-2018">
   <title>December 2018</title>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>Bugfixes</term>
     <listitem>
      <itemizedlist>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="CreateProfile-General-self-update"/>, clarified the
         <literal>self_update</literal> boot options and made descriptions
         consistent (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1121980"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="CreateProfile-General-self-update"/>, improved the
         description of the <literal>self_update</literal> attribute and fixed
         a typo in the example (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1119551"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="CreateProfile-Network-s390"/>, mentioned availability
         of option <literal>LLADDR</literal> on &zseries;
         (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1105195"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 xml:id="sec-ay-docupdates-sle15-sp0-oct-2018">
   <title>November 2018</title>
   <variablelist>
     <varlistentry>
      <term><xref linkend="configuration"/></term>
      <listitem>
       <para>Enhanced support for software RAID devices is available for
       &productname; 15. Added <xref linkend="ay-use-whole-disk"/> and updated 
       the software RAID documentation accordingly.</para>
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>Bugfixes</term>
     <listitem>
      <itemizedlist>
       <listitem>
        <para>
        In <xref linkend="Configuration-Security-groups"/>, added missing
         attribute for <tag>groups</tag> element.
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="scripts-syntax"/>, removed documentation of the
         obsolete <tag>network_needed</tag> attribute
         (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1094822"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="CreateProfile-General"/>, added a more comprehensive
         list of parameters that influence the installation workflow and split
         them into different categories. Also fixed a typo in
         <xref linkend="ex-general-common"/> (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1086175"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
       <para>
        In <xref linkend="CreateProfile-upgrade"/>, added a procedure about
        starting &ay; in upgrade mode and mentioned
        <filename>/root/autoupg.xml</filename> (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1047650"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 xml:id="sec-ay-docupdates-sle15-sp0-aug-2018">
   <title>August 2018</title>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>Bugfixes</term>
     <listitem>
      <itemizedlist>
       <listitem>
        <para> In <xref linkend="sec-ay-12vs15-product-selection"/>, fixed a
         typo in an example which lead to installation problems (<link
          xlink:href="&bsc;1104647"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>
         In <xref linkend="scripts-syntax"/>, clarify where to use
         <tag>chrooted</tag> and <tag>network_needed</tag> (<link
          xlink:href="&bsc;1094822"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>In <xref linkend="ay-partition-configuration"/>, added possible
         values for <literal>partition_id</literal> (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1094640"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para> In <xref linkend="Configuration-Security-users"/>, mentioned how
         to use encrypted passwords for users (<link xlink:href="&bsc;1071958"/>).
        </para>
       </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect2>
 </sect1>

</appendix>
